data.description: Dancing Bear Ranch welcomes you into your peaceful hill country living experience. Waking up to breathtaking hillside views and wildlife brings you closer to Mother Nature. The community pool sits on a hilltop over the horizon, perfect to experience sunsets. This lot offers plenty of space to build your custom home of your liking with a stunning view overlooking the hill country. Conveniently near the city for your local trips such as your grocery runs, shopping, etc. Community residents have private Lake Access which includes a Fishing Pier, Boat Ramp and Large Pavillon, great for gatherings. Take Texas living to another level!
